# Guardrails for this source-only public repository. They do not replace
# allow-list review, the publication preflight, or secret scanning.

# Local/private staging
/private/
/local/
/captures/
/diagnostics/
/artifacts/
/backups/
/backup/
**/backups/
**/backup/
**/router-backup*/
**/router-full-backup*/

